            <thetext>In qooxdoo qx.bom.client.OperatingSystem we use navigator.platform. Unify project told us, that they can not rely on this, as it does not return the right values on all platforms. They have implemented a class unify.bom.client.DeviceRuntime. Please improve qx.bom.client.OperatingSystem so that unify project does not need their own class anymore.</thetext>
